This directory contains fonts to support cairo drivers.

Vera.ttf - a Helvetica-like font
VeraBd.ttf - Vera bold
VeraIt.ttf - Vera Italic
VeraBI.ttf - Vera bold Italic
VeraMono.ttf - a Courier-like mono-spaced font
VeraMoBd.ttf - Vera mono bold
VeraMoIt.ttf - Vera mono Italic
VeraMoBI.ttf - Vera mono bold Italic
VeraSe.ttf - a times-like (Serif) font
VeraSeBd.ttf - Vera Serif bold
Aristarcoj2.ttf - Greek characters
cmex10.ttf - math symbols
cmsy10.ttf - some math, script


The site:

  http://www.freepremiumfonts.com/

has an amazing number of free fonts.

The Vera fonts are available with an open source license. See:

  http://www.bitstream.com/font_rendering/products/dev_fonts/vera.html
